test_list_of_single_number:
assert [] == [[78]]
  Right contains one more item: [78]
  Full diff:
  - [[78]]
  + []
test_list_of_several_same_number:
assert [] == [[78], [78], [78]]
  Right contains 3 more items, first extra item: [78]
  Full diff:
  - [[78], [78], [78]]
  + []
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 468 == 78
 +  where 468 = <built-in function prod>([1, 2, 3, 6, 13])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
